    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 inline-six, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline via six individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, while the factory limited-slip differential ensures optimal torque distribution. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings, preserving the chassis's renowned lateral stability and steering feedback. A mechanically sound example built for high-revving performance.",
