      "description": "This vehicle is a stellar example of pride of ownership, offering a reliable and aesthetically pleasing driving experience. The exterior paint retains a brilliant luster, accented by clean body lines, with only the minor, inevitable stone chips from careful highway use. Inside, the cabin feels fresh and inviting; the seating surfaces are supple and free of tears, while the dashboard and trim remain crack-free. All interior electronics, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no odd noises or leaks, backed by a consistent maintenance history. It handles beautifully with responsive steering and firm braking. This is a smoke-free, pet-free car that has been kept in a covered garage, making it an ideal choice for a buyer seeking a dependable, high-quality daily driver that looks and feels great.",
      "price": 32500.0,
