      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained specimen that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sophisticated styling. This vehicle has been curated for the discerning driver who prioritizes consistent performance and a well-preserved interior. Thoroughly inspected to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for roadworthiness and aesthetic appeal, this offering represents an exceptional balance of value and prestige. Experience the confidence of a vehicle that has been treated with the utmost care throughout its tenure.",
      "price": 34500.0,
